Here's how this fits your stack:
MySQL table:
sqlCREATE TABLE characters (
  id           BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id      VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  name         VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  class        VARCHAR(50),
  origin       VARCHAR(50),
  colour       VARCHAR(20),
  traits       VARCHAR(150),
