оБЦоАїоГїоГєоГОYou said: create a simple character  with name, strength etc and then user input, goal is to try get data to api and api to backend  - show this simplecreate a simple character  with name, strength etc and then user input, goal is to try get data to api and api to backend  - show this simple11:13оГОоБ§оБЦоАїClaude responded: Here's what's happening at each step:
  ::view-transition-group(*),
