Step 3 вАФ Write the code for each
java// model/Character.java
@Entity
@Table(name = "characters")
public class Character {

    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private Long id;

    private Long   userId;
    private String name;
    private int    age;
    private int    classId;
    private int    elementId;
    private String bio;
    private String artworkUrl;

    // right click вЖТ Generate вЖТ Getters and Setters
}
java// model/CharacterClass.java
@Entity
@Table(name = "class")
public class CharacterClass {

    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private int id;

    private String className;

    // right click вЖТ Generate вЖТ Getters and Setters
}
java// model/Element.java
@Entity
@Table(name = "element")
public class Element {

    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private int id;

    private String elementName;

    // right click вЖТ Generate вЖТ Getters and Setters
}
java// model/Stat.java
@Entity
@Table(name = "stats")
public class Stat {

    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private Long id;

    private Long characterId;
    private int  strength;
    private int  agility;
    private int  intelligence;
    private int  charisma;
    private int  endurance;

    // right click вЖТ Generate вЖТ Getters and Setters
}

Step 4 вАФ Generate Getters and Setters

Click inside the class
Right click
Click Generate
Click Getter and Setter
Select all fields
Click OK


Step 5 вАФ Add the imports at the top of each file
javaimport jakarta.persistence.Entity;
import jakarta.persistence.GeneratedValue;
import jakarta.persistence.GenerationType;
import jakarta.persistence.Id;
import jakarta.persistence.Table;

Your Model Folder Should Look Like This
model/
вФЬвФАвФА Character.java
вФЬвФАвФА CharacterClass.java
вФЬвФАвФА Element.java
вФФвФАвФА Stat.java

Golden Rule

Every model maps to one MySQL table
@Entity tells Spring Boot it is a database table
@Id marks the primary key
@GeneratedValue means MySQL auto generates the ID
Right click вЖТ Generate вЖТ saves you writing getters and setters manually
