Files Created
Controllers/
вФФвФАвФА CharacterController.java

DTOs/
вФФвФАвФА character/
    вФЬвФАвФА CharacterResponse.java
    вФФвФАвФА CreateCharacterRequest.java

repos/
вФФвФАвФА CharacterRepo.java

services/
вФФвФАвФА CharacterService.java

CharacterRepo.java

Interface that extends JpaRepository
Talks directly to the characters table in MySQL
Has one custom query вАФ findByUserId to get all characters for a user


CharacterService.java

Contains all the business logic for character management
Five methods:

getAll вАФ get all characters for a user
getOne вАФ get one character by ID
create вАФ save a new character
update вАФ update an existing character
delete вАФ delete a character




CharacterController.java

Exposes the REST endpoints the frontend will call
Five endpoints:

MethodEndpointWhat It DoesGET/api/characters/user/{userId}Get all characters for a userGET/api/characters/{id}Get one characterPOST/api/charactersCreate a characterPUT/api/characters/{id}Update a characterDELETE/api/characters/{id}Delete a character

CharacterResponse.java

DTO that controls what data gets sent OUT to the frontend
Fields: id, userId, name, age, classId, elementId, bio, artworkUrl


CreateCharacterRequest.java

DTO that controls what data comes IN from the frontend
Fields: userId, name, age, classId, elementId, bio, artworkUrl


How They Connect
Frontend
    вЖУ HTTP request
CharacterController   вЖР receives the request
    вЖУ
CharacterService      вЖР handles the logic
    вЖУ
CharacterRepo         вЖР talks to MySQL
    вЖУ
MySQL                 вЖР saves or retrieves the data
    вЖУ
CharacterResponse     вЖР sends data back to frontend

What Links To Other People's Work

Element вАФ Alisha's work
CharacterClass вАФ Bilal's work
Stat вАФ Bradley's work
User вАФ Edil's work
