javaprivate String name;   вЖР missing from model
private int age;       вЖР missing from model
Tell the team these need to be added to Character.java вАФ or add them yourself since they are character specific fields.

Do you need to create your own table?
No вАФ you do not create the table manually.
Spring Boot does it automatically when the app runs because of this line in application.properties:
propertiesspring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update
This tells Spring Boot to look at your Character.java model and create the characters table in MySQL automatically with all the right columns.

What MySQL will create automatically
sqlcharacters table
- id
- height
- weight
- element_id    вЖР foreign key
- class_id      вЖР foreign key
- stats_id      вЖР foreign key
- artwork
- name          вЖР once added
- age           вЖР once added

Simple answer

Add name and age to Character.java
No manual table creation needed
Spring Boot handles it all automatically
